                <p><span class="profile-label">特　徴：</span>ようかんが好き</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="retro-box about-me">
        <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="retro-decoration">■</span>
            ようかんについて
            <span class="retro-decoration">■</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="about-content">
            <p>ようかんです</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="retro-box recent-activities">
        <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="retro-decoration">●</span>
            最近の出来事
            <span class="retro-decoration">●</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="activity-list">
            <div class="activity-item">
                <div class="activity-date">2025年6月11日</div>
                <div class="activity-content">ホームページをリニューアルしました！</div>
            </div>
            <div class="activity-item">
                <div class="activity-date">2024年11月3日</div>
                <div class="activity-content">新商品を発売しました。</div>
            </div>
            <div class="activity-item">
                <div class="activity-date">2017年9月28日</div>
                <div class="activity-content">Discordアカウントを作りました</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="retro-box links">
        <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="retro-decoration">★</span>
            リンク集
            <span class="retro-decoration">★</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="link-list">
            <a href="#" class="retro-link">商品一覧</a>
            <a href="#" class="retro-link">通販サイト</a>
            <a href="#" class="retro-link">店舗案内</a>
            <a href="#" class="retro-link">お問い合わせ</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="visitor-counter">
        <p>あなたは <span class="counter">00001</span> 人目の訪問者です！</p>
    </div>
    
    <footer class="retro-footer">
        <p>Copyright © 2025 ようかん All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p class="best-viewed">このページは800x600以上の解像度で最適に表示されます</p>
    </footer>
</div>

<style>
    .profile-container {
        padding: 10px 0;
    }
    
    .profile-header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 30px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .profile-title {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin: 0 10px;
        color: var(--retro-accent-color);
    }
    
    .marquee {
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: #fff8dc;
        padding: 5px 0;
        border: 1px dashed var(--retro-border-color);
        margin: 20px 0 0;
    }
    
    .marquee-content {
        display: inline-block;
        white-space: nowrap;
        animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
        padding-left: 100%;
    }
    
    @keyframes marquee {
        0% { transform: translateX(0); }
        100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    }
    
    .profile-info {
        display: flex;
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }
    
    .profile-image-container {
        position: relative;
        width: 150px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .profile-image {
        width: 120px;
        height: 120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border: 3px solid var(--retro-border-color);
        overflow: hidden;
        background-color: #fff;
        position: relative;
    }
    
    .profile-avatar {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: #D2B48C;
    }
    
    .profile-initial {
        font-size: 60px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #8B4513;
    }
    
    
    .profile-details {
        flex-grow: 1;
    }
    
    .profile-nickname {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        font-weight: normal;
        color: #777;
    }
    
    .profile-meta {
        background-color: #fff8dc;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        border: 1px dashed var(--retro-border-color);
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    
    .profile-meta p {
        margin: 5px 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .profile-label {
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 70px;
    }
    
    .section-title {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 22px;
    }
    
    .about-content {
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    .highlight {
        background: linear-gradient(transparent 60%, #ffeb3b 60%);
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .activity-list {
        border-top: 1px dashed var(--retro-border-color);
    }
    
    .activity-item {
        display: flex;
        padding: 10px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--retro-border-color);
    }
    
    .activity-date {
        width: 120px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .activity-content {
        flex-grow: 1;
    }
    
    .link-list {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 15px;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .retro-link {
        display: block;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #fff8dc;
        border: 1px solid var(--retro-border-color);
        transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    
    .retro-link:hover {
        background-color: var(--retro-accent-color);
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    
    .visitor-counter {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 30px 0;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    
    .counter {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        background-color: #000;
        color: #0f0;
        font-family: monospace;
        border: 2px solid #444;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    
    .retro-footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #777;
        margin-top: 30px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--retro-border-color);
        padding-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .best-viewed {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .profile-info {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .profile-image-container {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .activity-item {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .activity-date {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    }
</style> 